z-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-su-kien-khai-truong-cua-hang-tai-ha-noi.html\/#VI_SAO_CAN_DICH_VU_TO_CHUC_SU_KIEN_KHAI_TRUONG\" title=\"V\u00cc SAO C\u1ea6N D\u1ecaCH V\u1ee4 T\u1ed4 CH\u1ee8C S\u1ef0 KI\u1ec6N KHAI TR\u01af\u01a0NG?\">V\u00cc SAO C\u1ea6N D\u1ecaCH V\u1ee4 T\u1ed4 CH\u1ee8C S\u1ef0 KI\u1ec6N KHAI TR\u01af\u01a0NG?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-su-kien-khai-truong-cua-hang-tai-ha-noi.html\/#QUY_TRINH_TO_CHUC_SU_KIEN_KHAI_TRUONG_CHUYEN_NGHIEP\" title=\"QUY TR\u00ccNH T\u1ed4 CH\u1ee8C S\u1ef0 KI\u1ec6N KHAI TR\u01af\u01a0NG CHUY\u00caN NGHI\u1ec6P\u00a0\">QUY TR\u00ccNH T\u1ed4 CH\u1ee8C S\u1ef0 KI\u1ec6N KHAI TR\u01af\u01a0NG CHUY\u00caN NGHI\u1ec6P\u00a0<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-su-kien-khai-truong-cua-hang-tai-ha-noi.html\/#_Tiep_nhan_thong_tin_khach_hang_va_tu_van\" title=\"\u00a0Ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n\">\u00a0Ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-su-kien-khai-truong-cua-hang-tai-ha-noi.html\/#Len_y_tuong_kich_ban_so_thao\" title=\"L\u00ean \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n s\u01a1 th\u1ea3o\">L\u00ean \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n s\u01a1 th\u1ea3o<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-su-kien-khai-truong-cua-hang-tai-ha-noi.html\/#Gui_bang_bao_gia_va_trao_doi_voi_khach_hang\" title=\"G\u1eedi b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng\">G\u1eedi b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-su-kien-khai-truong-cua-hang-tai-ha-noi.html\/#Lap_hop_dong_hoac_giay_xac_nhan_dich_vu\" title=\"L\u1eadp h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ho\u1eb7c gi\u1ea5y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5\">L\u1eadp h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ho\u1eb7c gi\u1ea5y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-su-kien-khai-truong-cua-hang-tai-ha-noi.html\/#Chuan_bi_nhan_su\" title=\"Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1\">Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-su-kien-khai-truong-cua-hang-tai-ha-noi.html\/#Tien_hanh_thuc_hien_su_kien\" title=\"Ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n\">Ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-su-kien-khai-truong-cua-hang-tai-ha-noi.html\/#Ket_thuc_su_kien_va_tong_hop_bao_cao\" title=\"K\u1ebft th\u00fac s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n v\u00e0 t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p b\u00e1o c\u00e1o\">K\u1ebft th\u00fac s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n v\u00e0 t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p b\u00e1o c\u00e1o<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><em><strong>T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/strong> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea5t k\u00ec doanh nghi\u1ec7p ho\u1eb7c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c n\u00e0y. Tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb cung c\u1ea5p <strong>d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/strong>. Tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u00e0o c\u0169ng cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng trong vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, <strong>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/strong> ra \u0111\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o d\u00e0nh cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u quy m\u00f4 kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/em><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"VI_SAO_CAN_DICH_VU_TO_CHUC_SU_KIEN_KHAI_TRUONG\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>V\u00cc SAO C\u1ea6N D\u1ecaCH V\u1ee4 T\u1ed4 CH\u1ee8C S\u1ef0 KI\u1ec6N KHAI TR\u01af\u01a0NG?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14688 \" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"955\" height=\"549\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi10.png 522w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi10-300x172.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 955px) 100vw, 955px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Ng\u00e0y l\u1ec5 khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng mang l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u00fac ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecbnh v\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi t\u1edbi tham d\u1ef1.L\u1ec5 khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng hay kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u1ed9i dung khi b\u1ea1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c. T\u1eeb kh\u00e2u ch\u1ecdn MC, \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u00f3m nh\u1ea3u, nh\u00f3m m\u00faa, PG l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u00e3y ch\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i th\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111i nh\u1eefng n\u1ed9i dung h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.<\/p>\n<p>K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng hay th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5\u00a0<strong><em>t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng<\/em><\/strong><strong>.<\/strong>\u00a0Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 m\u1ed7i c\u00f4ng ty lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng ri\u00eang v\u1ec1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ty s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 trong ng\u00e0nh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c cho r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n <strong><em>s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng\u00a0c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng<\/em><\/strong>,c\u00f4ng ty,kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n,nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng t\u1eeb quy m\u00f4 nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1edbn ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cung c\u1ea5p.C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean tr\u1ebb, nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media \u0111\u01b0a t\u1edbi qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i t\u1eeb l\u00ean \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ebfn d\u00e0n d\u1ef1ng ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh. M\u1ecdi c\u00f4ng \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0m chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1ef9 m\u00e3n. T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng mu\u1ed1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chu \u0111\u00e1o v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, do \u0111\u00f3, d\u00f9 b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c hay thu\u00ea m\u1ed9t b\u00ean d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7. B\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh hay, \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14683 \" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"643\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi4.jpg 900w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi4-300x201.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi4-768x515.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"QUY_TRINH_TO_CHUC_SU_KIEN_KHAI_TRUONG_CHUYEN_NGHIEP\"><\/span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: #ff0000;\">QUY TR\u00ccNH T\u1ed4 CH\u1ee8C S\u1ef0 KI\u1ec6N KHAI TR\u01af\u01a0NG CHUY\u00caN NGHI\u1ec6P\u00a0<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_Tiep_nhan_thong_tin_khach_hang_va_tu_van\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><em><span lang=\"EN-GB\">\u00a0Ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/span><\/em><\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c v\u00e0 h\u1ebft l\u00f2ng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1eb1m mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m m\u00e0 qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng d\u00e0nh cho c\u00f4ng ty.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Len_y_tuong_kich_ban_so_thao\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><em><span lang=\"EN-GB\">L\u00ean \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n s\u01a1 th\u1ea3o<\/span><\/em><\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 vi\u1ebft k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u1edbi v\u00f4 v\u00e0ng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o v\u00e0 m\u1edbi l\u1ea1 nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u00e2y d\u01b0ng th\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng theo d\u00f5i v\u00e0 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14681 \" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"971\" height=\"728\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi1.jpg 800w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi1-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi1-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 971px) 100vw, 971px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Gui_bang_bao_gia_va_trao_doi_voi_khach_hang\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><em><span lang=\"EN-GB\">G\u1eedi b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/span><\/em><\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111a d\u1ea1ng h\u00f3a g\u00f3i d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ecdi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng g\u1ee3i \u00fd h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Lap_hop_dong_hoac_giay_xac_nhan_dich_vu\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><em><span lang=\"EN-GB\">L\u1eadp h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ho\u1eb7c gi\u1ea5y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5<\/span><\/em><\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Khi ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\u1edbi qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c so\u1ea1n th\u1ea3o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chuan_bi_nhan_su\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><em><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1<\/span><\/em><\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-GB\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean h\u1ee3p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 theo \u0111\u00fang k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ra v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ph\u00e2n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-GB\">\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf: nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb, \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c n\u00ean s\u1ebd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 linh \u0111\u1ed9ng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0 di\u1ec5n ra s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tien_hanh_thuc_hien_su_kien\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><em><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/span><\/em><\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra theo \u0111\u00fang k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n v\u00e0 th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c<\/span><span lang=\"EN-GB\">\u00a0ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd nh\u1eefng r\u1ee7i ro b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi<\/span><span lang=\"EN-GB\">\u00a0b\u00e1m s\u00e1t ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ra th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14686 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1227\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi8.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi8-300x192.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi8-1024x654.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi8-768x491.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_khai_truong_cua_hang_tai_ha_noi8-1536x982.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_thuc_su_kien_va_tong_hop_bao_cao\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><em><span lang=\"EN-GB\">K\u1ebft th\u00fac s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n v\u00e0 t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p b\u00e1o c\u00e1o<\/span><\/em><\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh k\u1ebft th\u00fac l\u00e0 l\u00fac c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean vi\